@startuml Escalation_Path
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam shadowing false

title Escalation Path IT Incidents

rectangle "LEVEL 1\nStaff TI\n(Response Time: <2 jam)" as L1
rectangle "LEVEL 2\nManager TI\n(Critical Issues: <4 jam)" as L2
rectangle "LEVEL 3\nDirektur\n(Strategic Decisions: <24 jam)" as L3

L1 -down-> L2 : Escalate if:\n• Cannot resolve in 2h\n• Critical impact\n• Need approval
L2 -down-> L3 : Escalate if:\n• Strategic decision needed\n• Budget impact >Rp10jt\n• Business continuity risk

note right of L1
    Handles:
    • Routine incidents
    • User requests
    • Minor issues
end note

note right of L2
    Handles:
    • Complex technical issues
    • Risk assessment
    • Resource allocation
end note

note right of L3
    Handles:
    • Strategic decisions
    • Major investments
    • Crisis management
end note

@enduml
